                            My Coupons
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-12 w-full text-base sm:text-lg hover:text-blue-400 focus:text-blue-400 hover:bg-[#f5faff] mt-1">
                            My Reviews and ratings
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-12 w-full text-base sm:text-lg hover:text-blue-400 focus:text-blue-400 hover:bg-[#f5faff] mt-1">
                            All Notifications
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-12 w-full text-base sm:text-lg hover:text-blue-400 focus:text-blue-400 hover:bg-[#f5faff] mt-1">
